snippet.title: Old Time Hockey - New Year Teaser
snippet.description:
Happy New Year! We’ve received some fantastic feedback and responses since we announced our game. We’ve also received some concerns about our team representations so we’ve taken the opportunity to hit the drawing board and create some new teams! These teams are inspired from some of the birthplaces of hockey. We’ll reveal their logos soon but here’s the list to whet your appetite!

Schuylkill Hinto Brews - Pottsville, PA
Fort Edward Bluenosers - Windsor, NS
Long Island Rumrunners - Commack, NY
Quebec Voyous - Beauce, QC
Charlestown Stonemasons - Charlestown, MA
Warroad Ice Anglers - Warroad, MN
Cascadia Timber Cats  - Seattle, WA
Portage Lake Widowmakers - Houghton, MI
Moose Jaw Farmhands - Moose Jaw, SK
Cobalt Silvers - Cobalt, ON
